    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but seeking support doesn't really change the pattern. it's like... i do the work, i follow the advice, and i still end up right here. it’s not even about the setbacks anymore, it's just the sheer repetition of it all. i feel like i'm just waiting for the inevitable. it's like there's no actual way to break the loop without something drastic happening.",
